#This data is prepared each morning and contains information for the 
#projected peak of the day for areas within the PJM footprint. 
#Data is refreshed on top of the hour from 5 a.m. to 8 a.m.

#Posting Frequency: Daily
#Update Availability: Daily 05:00 a.m.
#Retention Time: Indefinitely

#trend analysis, forecast versus actual ploting, 
#twoway anova 
#multiple regression
